{"tid":2050590,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"無懼國安法西九龍「和你lunch」 市民呼籲：今晚維園見","createTime":"2020-06-04T08:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T08:58:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"06383ea0f7e17d840e03dbf880d60b5d03683938","tid":2050590,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:30:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200604/PV32S2JAJOY65J6U77M77MGRT4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200604%2FPV32S2JAJOY65J6U77M77MGRT4%2F&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=02e7a539\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200604%2FPV32S2JAJOY65J6U77M77MGRT4%2F&h=679b145b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200604/PV32S2JAJOY65J6U77M77MGRT4/</a><br />\n<br />\n無懼國安法西九龍「和你lunch」 市民呼籲：今晚維園見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://thumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub/IcRXNdIMB19udqqLqprIxeUNhgQ=/arc-photo-appledaily/ap-ne-1-prod/public/CUIDNGQNNG4EDE36CB7XTOFOHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub%2FIcRXNdIMB19udqqLqprIxeUNhgQ%3D%2Farc-photo-appledaily%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FCUIDNGQNNG4EDE36CB7XTOFOHQ.jpg&h=8d98786a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民在圓方商場和你lunch。<br />\n<br />\n【14:05】市民最後以「平反六四 今晚維園見」口號作結，結束「和你lunch 」活動。<br />\n【13:56】揮動旗幟的市民離開演薈廣場，返回商場內，繼續喊叫口號，「釋放義士 還我公義」、「7.21唔見人 8.31打死人」。<br />\n【13:39】數名市民到達演薈廣場，高叫口號「一息尚存、抗爭到底」，「平反六四 刻不容緩」、「六四 維園見」，圍觀的市民聚集廣場位置，部份跟隨叫口號。有市民揮舞一支疑似英屬香港旗。 <br />\n【13:30】市民乘電梯登上各樓層，繼續叫喊口號，「為仔仔孫孫平安 香港人加油」，同時高舉「五大訴求、缺一不可」的手勢。由於正值午飯時間，不少上班一族圍觀，暫未見有警員到場。<br />\n【13:20】約十名市民在圓方商場「遊行」，並高唱「願榮光歸香港」，高叫口號「光復香港 時代革命」、「五大訴求 缺一不可」，有市民喊叫「黑警害死香港人」、「全民三罷」、「香港人加油」。<br />\n<br />\n中共通過。。。。。。。。。。。。。。」，繼續發聲抗惡法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n打國際線 《蘋果》英文版免費試睇 按此了解更多<br />\n英文版已登錄新版《蘋果》App按此下載/更新<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 立即WhatsApp《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線 或致電：63836568<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民高舉五大訴求，缺一不可手勢。<br />\n<br />\n有市民揮舞疑似英屬香港旗幟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨着午飯時間過去，圍觀市民逐漸散去。<br />\n<br />\n市民慢慢離開廣場。<br />\n<br />\n市民最後以「平反六四 今晚維園見」口號作結。[/quote]"},{"pid":"3dfd6536663a51aa5d3158f06892b0a76d9e273d","tid":2050590,"uid":116917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:41:14.000Z","msg":"維園見"},{"pid":"fcac83dbf0ca24449040c5db90d889db21bc8da9","tid":2050590,"uid":277992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:43:53.000Z","msg":"睇立場話維園足球場比狗封左？"},{"pid":"737e274dd0478d2bbc9315428446ef83bdb46b7e","tid":2050590,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:52:11.000Z","msg":"[思想武裝]我們不妨功利一點看待｢六四｣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2049910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2049910</a>"},{"pid":"a23179805958812933f77345c49c306cb77fa40a","tid":2050590,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcac83dbf0ca24449040c5db90d889db21bc8da9","tid":2050590,"uid":277992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:43:53.000Z","msg":"睇立場話維園足球場比狗封左？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:57:04.000Z","msg":"太多人入唔到維園係咪即係要企出， 糖街， 記利佐治街， 高士威道， 興發街 ，電氣道嗰啲 ？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOk, 我企呢啲位無問題， 如果入唔到維園既話。"},{"pid":"a0e391563e0be8824a9ddca31402d055b27f9ce8","tid":2050590,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a23179805958812933f77345c49c306cb77fa40a","tid":2050590,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcac83dbf0ca24449040c5db90d889db21bc8da9","tid":2050590,"uid":277992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:43:53.000Z","msg":"睇立場話維園足球場比狗封左？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:57:04.000Z","msg":"太多人入唔到維園係咪即係要企出， 糖街， 記利佐治街， 高士威道， 興發街 ，電氣道嗰啲 ？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOk, 我企呢啲位無問題， 如果入唔到維園既話。"}